title: RDPB sets up 47 Sufficiency Economy Learning Centers nationwide (Royal Thai Government)
text: ( Source : Royal Thai Government ) October 12 , 2015 , at 0930hrs, at the Green Room , Thai Ku Fah Building , Government House , Prime Minister Gen Prayut Chan-o-cha presided over the 1/2015 meeting of the Royal Development Projects Board (RDPB).
